    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241258",
        "quote": "The more we pour the big machines, the fuel, the pesticides, the herbicides, the fertilizer and chemicals into farming, the more we knock out the mechanism that made it all work in the first place.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David R. Brower",
            "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241258"
