    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241250",
        "quote": "All I know about thermal pollution is that if we continue our present rate of growth in electrical energy consumption it will simply take, by the year 2000, all our freshwater streams to cool the generators and reactors.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David R. Brower",
            "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241250"
