                "url": "/topics/pacific_ocean"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241266",
        "quote": "We've got to search back to our last known safe landmark. I can't say exactly where, but I think it's back there at the start of the Industrial Revolution, we began applying energy in vast amounts to tools with which we began tearing the environment apart.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David R. Brower",
            "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241266"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Back",
                "url": "/topics/back"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Got",
                "url": "/topics/got"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241261",
        "quote": "What's even more unsettling is the way these people hide what they're doing from the public. They strip the labels off miracle wheat when they ship it, for instance, and say, 'Watch out. Don't plant too much and don't depend on it too much.'",
        "author": {
            "name": "David R. Brower",
            "url": "/quotes/david_r_brower_241261"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
